{"name": "nonebot-plugin-moyu", "metadata": {"name": "nonebot-plugin-moyu", "version": "0.3.4", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["nonebot-adapter-onebot", "nonebot-plugin-apscheduler", "nonebot2"], "summary": "View your moyu calendar in NoneBot2", "upload_time": 1733222583}, "documentation": ["<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://v2.nonebot.dev/store\"><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/nbp_logo.png\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginLogo\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <p><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/NoneBotPlugin.svg\" width=\"240\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginText\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n# nonebot-plugin-moyu\n\n_\u2728 \u6478\u9c7c\u4e00\u65f6\u723d, \u4e00\u76f4\u6478\u9c7c\u4e00\u76f4\u723d \u2728_\n\n\n<a href=\"./LICENSE\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-moyu.svg\" alt=\"license\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot-plugin-moyu\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nonebot-plugin-moyu.svg\" alt=\"pypi\">\n</a>\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg\" alt=\"python\">\n\n</div>\n\n## \ud83d\udcbf \u5b89\u88c5\n\n<details>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528 nb-cli \u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u8f93\u5165\u4ee5\u4e0b\u6307\u4ee4\u5373\u53ef\u5b89\u88c5\n\n    nb plugin install nonebot-plugin-moyu\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668\u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\u5728 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684\u63d2\u4ef6\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b, \u6253\u5f00\u547d\u4ee4\u884c, \u6839\u636e\u4f60\u4f7f\u7528\u7684\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668, \u8f93\u5165\u76f8\u5e94\u7684\u5b89\u88c5\u547d\u4ee4\n\n<details>\n<summary>pip</summary>\n\n    pip install nonebot-plugin-moyu\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>pdm</summary>\n\n    pdm add nonebot-plugin-moyu\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>poetry</summary>\n\n    poetry add nonebot-plugin-moyu\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>conda</summary>\n\n    conda install nonebot-plugin-moyu\n</details>\n\n\u6253\u5f00 nonebot2 \u9879\u76ee\u7684 `bot.py` \u6587\u4ef6, \u5728\u5176\u4e2d\u5199\u5165\n\n    nonebot.load_plugin('nonebot_plugin_moyu')\n\n</details>\n\n## \ud83c\udf89 \u4f7f\u7528\n### \u6307\u4ee4\u8868\n| \u6307\u4ee4  | \u8bf4\u660e |\n|:-----:|:----:|\n| \u6478\u9c7c/\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386 | \u67e5\u770b\u4eca\u5929\u7684\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386 |\n| \u6478\u9c7c/\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386+\u8bbe\u7f6e | \u4ee5\u8fde\u7eed\u5bf9\u8bdd\u7684\u5f62\u5f0f\u8bbe\u7f6e\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386\u7684\u63a8\u9001\u65f6\u95f4 |\n| \u6478\u9c7c/\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386+\u8bbe\u7f6e \u5c0f\u65f6:\u5206\u949f | \u8bbe\u7f6e\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386\u7684\u63a8\u9001\u65f6\u95f4 |\n| \u6478\u9c7c/\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386+\u72b6\u6001 | \u67e5\u770b\u672c\u7fa4\u7684\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386\u72b6\u6001 |\n| \u6478\u9c7c/\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386+\u7981\u7528 | \u7981\u7528\u672c\u7fa4\u7684\u6478\u9c7c\u65e5\u5386\u63a8\u9001 |\n"], "modules": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_moyu", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_moyu.save_subscribe", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_moyu.get_calendar", "asynchronous": true, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_moyu.subscribe_jobs", "asynchronous": true, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_moyu.push_calendar", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "group_id", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_mo